You are controlling the text style under this condition, `inbox.getRead().equals(&quot;read&quot;)`, but you are not actually changing the value of your `read` value in the inbox object. 

What you should do is, you should change the value of `read` property of your `inbox` object at the particular position, and then call `notifyItemChanged(position);`.

You should do something like this, 

    public void Unread(int position) {
        this.list.get(position).setRead(&quot;unread&quot;);
        notifyItemChanged(position);
    }

This should change the `read` in your `inbox` object, and should work for you.

